Ubit cash is blockchain-based smart contract (ERC20) built on the most powerful blockchain technology named “Ethereum”,
it's ghost protocol allows faster transaction times and capable to grow and adapt to the needs of the community.

Ubit Cash set “High Ethical Standards” in business and to leave no stone unturned in order to implementation of latest technological advancement & business development.

The project is designed with meticulous attention to accomplish business goals, success and to satisfy customers. We are open-minded, flexible and honest in our dealings and committed to ethical behavior, accountability and transparency.
